# CarbonSense Project Overview

CarbonSense is a comprehensive system for carbon footprint data analysis powered by IBM watsonx.ai. The system processes, analyzes, and provides insights into carbon footprint data from various sources.

## Core Components

### Main Entry Points
- [src/carbonsense/main.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/main.py) - Main CLI interface for running different modes
- [src/carbonsense/web/run_server.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/run_server.py) - Starts the web dashboard interface
- [src/carbonsense/web/app.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/app.py) - FastAPI web application

### Core Functionality
- [src/carbonsense/core/crew_agent.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/core/crew_agent.py) - Multi-agent orchestration with CrewAI
- [src/carbonsense/core/carbon_agent.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/core/carbon_agent.py) - Standard RAG agent implementation
- [src/carbonsense/core/carbon_flow.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/core/carbon_flow.py) - Query processing pipeline
- [src/carbonsense/core/embedding_generator.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/core/embedding_generator.py) - Generates embeddings for vector search
- [src/carbonsense/core/yaml_manager.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/core/yaml_manager.py) - YAML configuration management

